---
title: Quick Sweet-Soy Beef & Broccoli Noodles with Crispy Shallots
description: beef and noodles - it’s one of those epic comfort-food combos that always goes down a treat. This meal is full of savoury Asian flavours, with sweet soy seasoning on the chicken and Korean stir-fry sauce stirred through the noodles and veggies. Add a sprinkle of crispy shallots for a touch of crunch and dig in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
